Oculus has launched big discounts on its Rift headset and Touch motion controllers. The Rift headset bundled with two Touch controllers is now priced at $399. The previous price was $598. An Xbox One wireless controller is also included in the Rift + Touch bundle. The Oculus Touch controllers allow gamers to interact with their VR world using gestures and motion control. The new pricing will only be available for a limited time and Oculus did not state when the special will end. 